id=seiran_sysctl_guard
name=Seiran Sysctl Guard
version=v0.0.2
versionCode=20260706
author=superuseryu
description=Re-applies vm.* sysctl + zram sizing post-boot that ROM init.rc/vendor perf-hal silently override. WebUI: pick TCP congestion control, check RAM/ZRAM, see whether guard defaults are actually applied. No governor forcing.
